vote.title: Authorize acquisition from Jose Luis DeLeon and Maria DeLeon, of approximately 5,252 square feet of land improved with a single-family dwelling located near the intersection of Alex and Childers Streets for the Cadillac Heights Phase II Project - Not to exceed $68,000.00 ($65,000.00, plus closing costs not to exceed $3,000.00) - Financing: Land Acquisition in Cadillac Heights (2006 General Obligation Bond Fund)
